<item>
            <title>[JDK-8306983] Do not invoke external programs when switch terminal to raw mode on selected platforms</title>
                <link>https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8306983</link>
                <project id="10100" key="JDK">JDK</project>
                    <description>(On non-Windows platforms:) currently, when jdk.internal.le (which is the JLine 3 library) switches terminal to raw mode, it will call several external programs to do that.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
The task herein is to avoid the invocation of external programs on selected platforms by directly invoking the native functions that would switch the terminal.&lt;br/&gt;
</description>
